txt.en: Thank you for contributing your collection! Please place your items in the box to receive your reward.
Wanted: Broken wooden maces from goblins to the east of Amon Raith. Deliver the items to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith.
'William will be pleased to see that this has been done. Thank you.'

'The Ranger there, Amarion, is doing what he can, but William wants to do more. We are simple people though not seasoned adventurers and warriors. Perhaps you would be willing to drive the goblins back and provide a little proof.'
DNT HIDING CONTENT - Task: Broken Wooden Maces
Nathan Hodges, at Amon Raith, awaits the collection and delivery of broken wooden maces.
Deliver the broken wooden maces to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith
Wanted: Broken wooden maces from goblins to the east of Amon Raith.
